Weixin::Client v2.1
========================
该项目已经停止维护，请关注重构项目 https://github.com/sjdy521/Mojo-Weixin

使用Perl语言编写的微信客户端框架，普通微信号(非公众号)手机扫码登录, 和手机客户端同时在线，消息自动同步

INSTALLATION:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

   or 

   cpan -i Weixin::Client

DEPENDENCIES:
   
    JSON
    AnyEvent::HTTP
    LWP::UserAgent
    LWP::Protocol::https

